Repository Notice
=================

This repository runs against upstream NautilusTrader from PyPI and keeps local
Nautilus-derived runtime extensions under `prediction_market_extensions/`.

Licensing scope
---------------

- `prediction_market_extensions/` and other files that carry a Nautilus-derived
  notice are also distributed under LGPL-3.0-or-later.
- Root files without that notice remain under the MIT License unless they say
  otherwise.
- Flat notebook runners under `backtests/` are not LGPL-covered just because
  they import repo code; only files listed below or carrying Nautilus-derived
  provenance notices fall under the LGPL scope here.

