Upstream lineage
----------------

- NautilusTrader upstream project: `https://github.com/nautechsystems/nautilus_trader`
- This repository uses upstream `nautilus_trader` as the active runtime
  dependency.
- Local extensions live under `prediction_market_extensions/` in their own
  namespace, importing from and subclassing upstream base classes.
- The earlier vendored NautilusTrader tree was removed from the worktree on this
  branch; provenance for that prior import remains available in git history.
